  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Triangle R has an area of <math alttext=\"80 square centimeters left parenthesis cm squared right parenthesis\"><mrow><mn>80</mn></mrow><mo>&#160;</mo><mtext>square</mtext><mo>&#160;</mo><mtext>centimeters</mtext><mo>&#160;</mo><mfenced><msup><mtext>cm</mtext><mn>2</mn></msup></mfenced></math>. Square S has side lengths of <math alttext=\"4 cm\"><mrow><mn>4</mn></mrow><mo>&#160;</mo><mtext>cm</mtext></math>. What is the total area of triangle R and square S, <math alttext=\"in cm squared\"><mtext>in</mtext><mo>&#160;</mo><msup><mtext>cm</mtext><mn>2</mn></msup></math>?</p>",
